snippet.textDisplay:
1) Kachiyyan te rakhiye naa umeed paar di 
"Kacha" refers to material things such as your body and mind, which constantly strive for survival and pleasure. However, if you solely follow the desires of your mind, it will only lead to temporary mental gratification.

1) Kacha Ghara refers to Human-Body
2) the other character is Sprit(rooh)
3) the river is hardship of this world 
4) "Kulli" is some super natural 
This song is great communication between all these characters
